{
  "stem": "9156.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I felt that this was maybe-- I didn't feel as close to them as to the old youth movement, but I would be part of it, and I would have something-- what I liked there, especially, was the great mixture, and really, a mixture, of intellectuals and working people.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we would.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were all these evenings where one would discuss things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was learning a lot about working class problems.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this particular group, for instance, it was not for collectivization of the farmland, but they were for cutting down the big farm-- the landowners.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they belonged to a group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a famous professor, Oppenheim, O-P-P-E-N-H-E-I-M, who had the theory that one can work with small farmers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm just giving examples.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We learned a lot about economics.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We learned a lot about thinking, Socratic method-- how do you really think about problems?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was a lot of-- I-- and strange things, perhaps, today, but for us, some very important.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I grew up in the west of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had been, a lot, in the east because many of my relatives were very poor and lived in the eastern part of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, I have to say-- and I say things at the side-- that I never understood the separation of Western and Eastern Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean-- [LAUGHS] But I had grown up in the western part of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they made us-- they said we should sit for a day and a night in one of those awful movies on the, on the part in the slums of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And sit there and see what goes on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was very important, because we saw, suddenly, that these were all people, sitting in those movies, who had no place to live.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
